gonna find us.

01:30:17.121 --> 01:30:18.206
Okay.

01:30:19.248 --> 01:30:20.874
Sparrow was working
for Levritt...

01:30:20.875 --> 01:30:22.042
Yeah.

01:30:22.043 --> 01:30:24.169
But he was the one
that switched the tape,

01:30:24.170 --> 01:30:26.088
and he didn't help me
when I needed it.

01:30:26.089 --> 01:30:28.507
