line 15.

01:35:03.366 --> 01:35:05.993
There are two ways
out of this, Lucas.

01:35:06.619 --> 01:35:09.288
One is you can withdraw
your challenge.

01:35:09.789 --> 01:35:11.290
And the other?

01:35:12.249 --> 01:35:16.420
