this one thing.

01:35:42.613 --> 01:35:45.533
Was Will Beckford still alive
when I left the ritual room?

01:35:46.158 --> 01:35:47.743
Son, I love you,

01:35:48.160 --> 01:35:50.287
and I've never lied
to you.

01:35:51.706 --> 01:35:53.082
