01:36:10.725 --> 01:36:13.686
Gentlemen,
it's time to begin.

01:36:28.534 --> 01:36:30.368
Mr. Mandrake,
you have been challenged,

01:36:30.369 --> 01:36:33.080
therefore the choice
of weapons is yours.

01:36:48.888 --> 01:36:51.182
Gentlemen,
take your positions.

01:37:01.484 --> 01:37:02.943
Back to back.

01:37:11.660 --> 01:37:13.579
